  </div>
  <div>
    <img src="../public/assets/crown.svg" alt="My Image" class="scroll-image2 rotate-image" />
  </div>
  <div>
    <img src="../public/assets/skull.svg" alt="My Image" class="scroll-image3 rotate-image" />
  </div>
  <div>
    <img src="../public/assets/chess.svg" alt="My Image" class="scroll-image4 rotate-image" />
  </div>
  <div>
    <p class="quote">
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Sunt, illo molestiae? Aliquam dolorem illum praesentium, delectus voluptates aperiam. Commodi modi soluta velit facere explicabo autem ipsam quo asperiores illo officiis.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
